column12:
'desc': [u'

Lavos Men's Brief Price: Rs.299

Step out with confidence and ease on a sunny day by wearing these black and grey briefs under your trousers. These solid briefs from the esteemed fashion house of Lavos are made from a blend of organic bamboo cotton and elastane to give you ultimate comfort and a relaxed feel all day long. Being anti-fungal and anti-odour in nature
column13: these sport briefs keep you cooler at 5 degree Celsius than outside temperature and protect your skin from harmful UV rays. Made of soft material
column14: this pair of briefs is perfectly finished with a panel detail
column15:
a logo woven on the elastic waistband and a contoured pouch with stitch detail.

\r\n

\r\n\tWith insights about comfort needs of its customers
column16:
Lavos innovates new techniques to infuse a value in every little intricacy of innerwear it crafts; you get to experience comfort like never before.

Fabric Care

Keep the garment looking as good as new for longer by machine washing these briefs at 40 degree Celsius and tumble drying them on low. Do not bleach.
